<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>搬一次家可真不容易。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从芝加哥这样的大城市搬到一个小山村就更不容易了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们来问问巴斯家的孩子们吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里没什么好玩的！”名叫赛伊的老大抱怨道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里什么商店都没有。”老二安西娅也在抱怨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的兄弟姐妹亲切地叫她潘瑟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那时，她的弟弟鲍比年纪很小。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他还不会叫安西娅，所以他就叫她潘瑟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在其他几个兄弟姐妹也这么叫她了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您这是什么意思？我们不能上网？”鲍比哭着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咦！那是什么？”简尖叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77800</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只棕色的小田鼠从台阶下迅速跑出来，冲进了草从里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有一个人想要搬到玛莎阿姨的家里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但爸爸丢掉了工作，他们没有其他的选择了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们坐在餐桌边妈妈尽力安慰他们说：“我们就在这里小住几天。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里有很多事情可以做。”玛莎阿姨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对啊，比如抓蚱蜢。”赛伊没好气的说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130000</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蚱蜢？哪里？”简尖叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>更糟糕的是，妈妈和爸爸第二天一早就离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸要去芝加哥参加几个工作面试。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们孤孤单单地站在台阶上，看着小汽车慢慢开走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咩，咩。”小婴儿开心地大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，兰姆。没什么事情能让你觉得伤心，对不对？”潘瑟笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小婴儿希拉里会有这个昵称是因为它说的第一个词是“咩”，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就像小羊羔一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178974</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们不想回到房子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183005</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那里什么也没得玩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨家后面是一片茂密的森林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为没人有更好的主意了，于是他们就出发去森林里探险了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！”鲍比激动地指着一大群浣熊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“闻闻！”潘瑟一边说一边弯下腰去闻这些美丽的花朵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一整天，孩子们都在森林里搜索新的发现。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，他们发现自己身在茂密的丛林中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里黑的好可怕。”潘瑟有点儿担心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“或者我们应该回去了。”简补充道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿！看这个！”赛伊激动地大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251139</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊发现了一口古老的枯井。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251140</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你能看到什么东西吗？”简问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有人都弯腰向井里看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有！但是我感觉这里面会很有趣。”赛伊回答说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“里面有水吗？”鲍比问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们盯着井里更深的地方，他们的眼睛越睁越大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在想这会不会是一个许愿井。”简说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等！看这里。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟在枯井的旁边发现了一个破旧的木桶系在绳子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301341</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们把这个桶放到井里去，看看那下面有什么吧。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她在干嘛？”鲍比指着简说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319295</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简闭上了眼睛，拿着一枚硬币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在许愿。”她回答说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她转身将硬币越过肩膀扔进了井里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>叮当！叮当！叮当！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>337889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呦！”井里传出一声大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>337890</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>343318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们听见了吗？”鲍比小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>343319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>350320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，下面的！”赛伊大声叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>350321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>356771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，下面的！”他的声音在井里回荡着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>356772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>361790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后一切都安静了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>361791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>367365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我肯定我听到了的声音。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>367366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>373162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你觉得那是动物吗？”简担心地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>373163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>379186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要找到答案就只有一个方法。”赛伊激动地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>379187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>383704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他将桶向下放到了井里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>383705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>387471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你能感觉到什么吗？”潘瑟问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>387472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>394192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快点，你能感觉到什么吗？”鲍比耐不住性子地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>394193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>397508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊将桶拉了回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>397509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>404368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>桶里满是泥巴、汽水罐、旧鞋子，还有一些石头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>404369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>410582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊又将木桶放到井底好几次。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>410583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>419173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果井里有什么东西，他下定决心一定要把它找出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>